Copyright (C) 2014 Ayan Chakrabarti, William T. Freeman, Todd Zickler.

This is a reference implementation of the algorithms described in our
paper:

Ayan Chakrabarti, William T. Freeman, and Todd Zickler, "Rethinking
Color Cameras," Proceedings of the IEEE International Conference on
Computational Photography, 2014.

This source code is currently being made available for non-commercial
research use only.

Please run compile, and then look at demo.m for a how to use.

The sample image is from the Gehler et al. database, reprocessed by
Shi, as referred to in the paper. Please use this code only with
linear images and not tone-mapped / gamma-corrected ones.